song.title: Imajica
song.info:
basehead/ImpCda - 19 November 1994
samples from a yamaha dx7, roland r8, jogeir, necros, sidewinder, and alpha. greets to maj, nec, khy and all #trax-ers. i know this song kind of bites, because of the generic "demo" style thru most of it but i think it's good listening music, regardless... - bh94!impcda/klf/ice -
